  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM11.10">
<l>cemmai yuṭaiya tiruvaraṅkar tāmpaṇitta</l>
<l>meymmaip peruvārttai viṭṭucittar kēṭṭiruppar,</l>
<l>tammai yukappārait tāmukappa reṉṉuñcol,</l>
<l>tammiṭaiyē poyyāṉāl cātippā rāriṉiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Viṣṇucitta would hear the great words of truth</l>
<l>Uttered by the upright Raṅganātha,</l>
<l>That “He loves those who love Him”:</l>
<l> If [these] words prove false in her matter, who can now establish [them]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
